# Binaries
*.exe
*.test
*.prof

# Go
vendor/
go.work
go.work.sum

# IDE
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Secrets (never commit)
agent-keys.txt
**/secrets/
!internal/secrets/
!/internal/secrets/*.go
*.pem
*.crt
*.key

# Runtime artifacts
*.log
feedback.log

# Config (use config.example/ as template)
# Every live per-workspace config + operation catalog is ignored generically:
# they carry real hostnames, emails, token hashes, and cluster/env/group ids.
# The workspace token is the `<x>` in config.<x>.yaml / operations.<x>.yaml.
# All root-anchored (leading /) so config.example/ templates stay tracked.
/config.yaml
/secrets.yaml
/config.*.yaml
/operations.*.yaml

# Local domain knowledge (workspace specifics, tokens, URLs)
.ai/LOCAL.md

# Build / deploy
dist/

# Temp
tmp/
